title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 3 2021

description:
Buck flies solo on Open Line Friday. Tired old Joe spins incredibly weak jobs report. Experts wrong again, only 235,000 jobs added vs. expectations of 720,000. Senator Joe Manchin: Congress needs to take a strategic pause, why I won’t support spending another $3.5 trillion. Fact Check of USA Today's Fact Check: Yes, Biden Looked at His Watch. Fauci's latest flip-flop: 3-shot regimen is all you need!
